				<EmbeddedObject>
					<Id>9991001001</Id>
					<Name><![CDATA[ashTransportToBrickKiln]]></Name>
					<Description><![CDATA[COMBUSTION DES — Step 5/7: Ash transport to brick kiln (tri 1, 2, 4 h). Internal BIWASE logistics: forklift movement of ash/slag hopper to tunnel kiln area. ESCAR: ash collected every 90-120 min by forklift (Photo 4, p.115). Entry action stages stagingAshCycleMass_t. Only bottom ash fraction (bottomAsh_massFraction=0.25) continues to brickProduction; fly ash (0.04) routes via flyAshToLandfill.]]></Description>
					<X>750</X><Y>310</Y>
					<Label><X>-70</X><Y>-18</Y></Label>
					<PublicFlag>false</PublicFlag>
					<PresentationFlag>true</PresentationFlag>
