				<EmbeddedObject>
					<Id>9983001001</Id>
					<Name><![CDATA[pwStart]]></Name>
					<Description><![CDATA[PROCESS WASTE DES — Step 1/4: Source (visualization only). Fired monthly by recyclingProcessing() via pwStart.inject() when process waste > 0. This DES does NOT model physical truck transport — the GarbageTruck agent handles external collection. It visualizes what happens to recycling residue (process waste) already inside BIWASE after processing. Chain: pwStart → pwTransport (internal bin movement, 1–4 h) → pwLandfillDeposit (deposit at Da Phuoc landfill, 0.5–2 h) → pwSink (LCA impacts applied from pw_pending* buffers). Tonnage and LCA values are staged in pw_pending* variables before injection.]]></Description>
					<X>410</X><Y>540</Y>
					<Label><X>-70</X><Y>-18</Y></Label>
