				<EmbeddedObject>
					<Id>9983001003</Id>
					<Name><![CDATA[pwLandfillDeposit]]></Name>
					<Description><![CDATA[PROCESS WASTE DES — Step 3/4: Landfill deposit delay (tri 0.5, 1, 2 h). Represents the formal deposit at Da Phuoc Sanitary Landfill: weighbridge check-in, cell routing, compaction, and daily cover. The split between landfill and incineration is controlled by pw_landfillSharePerMat[m] and pw_incinerationSharePerMat[m], set in recyclingProcessing() before injection. Residual fraction (1 - landfill - incineration) is logged as pw_toOther (future IS output / unspecified fate).]]></Description>
					<X>565</X><Y>530</Y>
					<Label><X>-70</X><Y>-18</Y></Label>
					<PublicFlag>false</PublicFlag>
					<PresentationFlag>true</PresentationFlag>
