					<Name><![CDATA[pollTimer]]></Name>
					<Description><![CDATA[CE3.0 dispatch heartbeat: fires every 6 sim-hours in GarbageTruck's own event context. Sole purpose: give AnyLogic a reason to re-evaluate condition-triggered transitions for this agent — specifically t_dispatch (condition: dispatchPending). Without this, an idle truck has no internal events and AnyLogic never checks dispatchPending after external code sets it (from Intermediate.acceptBooking or Provider retry/NonIS events). Action is intentionally empty; the condition re-evaluation is automatic after any agent event.]]></Description>
					<X>60</X><Y>1050</Y>
